# patch-package diffs must keep their committed (LF) line endings byte-for-byte:
# node_modules sources are LF, and a CRLF-converted checkout (core.autocrlf=true,
# set when this repo lived on Windows) makes every hunk context mismatch, so
# `npm install` silently builds an UNPATCHED expo-audio. Found in audit Phase 0.
*.patch -text
